Class NcbiTaxonomy

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mpa.analysis.taxonomy.NcbiTaxonomy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class NcbiTaxonomy
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This class constructs an index file for the taxonomy (phylogentic tree) from NCBI: ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pub/taxonomy/taxdmp.zip
    Author:
    R. Heyer, T. Muth
    See Also:
